description:
CloudStruct was founded by senior professional **operations engineers** and **open source developers**.

Our engineers have experience at companies like Box, Oracle, Yahoo, Microsoft, and Apple. We have decades of hands-on expertise running **global scale** infrastructure, telecommunications, distributed data systems, and low latency/high-throughput services with users in the billions. We have been involved in various open source ecosystems from Gentoo Linux to Chef to Ansible.

Check out our open source projects on **[GitHub](https://github.com/cloudstruct)** or join the conversation on our **[Discord server](https://discord.gg/5fPRZnX4qW)**.
